    /// Generated unparser, callable from Python.
    ///
    /// Each `unparse_{rule}` method runs the full pipeline (unparse -> resolve ->
    /// render) over a Rust-CST handle and returns the formatted string. It accepts
    /// only the Rust-backed `Py{ClassName}` handles, so a Python caller must pair
